translated: Ahlstrin, Ivar Selmer, director, Gothenburg, b. 30/7/90 in Gothenburg to merchant Gustaf Ad. Larson and Selma Elvira Alstrin. Married for 17 years to Ellen Maria Lindberg. Children: Nina Signe b. 31. Worked for Gbgs Spannmåls- & Foderämnes A-B 08-09, Gustaf Fagerberg 09-10, L. & R. Philip 10-16, Fallenius & Lefflers A-B 16, appointed deputy managing director in 24, and managing director in A-B Godstrafik & Bilspedition and In-tersped A-B since 18. Serves: as board member of Fallenius & Lefflers A-B in Gbg since 24, A-B Godstrafik & Bilspedition, Intersped A-B since 18, Sv. Speditions A-B in Trelleborg since 40, Holmens Magasins A-B since 28, Malmö Bilspeditions A-B since 36, Norrköp. Bilspeditions A-B since 37, Örebro Bilspeditions A-B 37-42, Jönköp. Bilspeditions A-B since 38, Eskilstuna Bilspeditions A-B since 41, Sthtos Bifepeditions A-B 35-42, Bilspedition in Gbg A-B 45, A-B Varutrafik 42, A-B Godsemottagning in Gbgs Hamn 28 and Verkst. A-B Domus 45, chairman and treasurer of Sv:es bilgods-speditörers fören. 36-44, board member and treasurer of Långedrags villaägare-fören. 36-45, board member and treasurer of Gbgs köpmäns arb :giv iförb. since 37, vice-chairman since 46, board member of Gbgs speditörsfören. since 42, vice-chairman since 46, board member of Svies isped:fören. riks’förb. since 46 and Gbgs omlastningsfören. u. p. a. since 42, member of Gbgs hamns trafikkomm. since 40, Ehrenamtl. Korresp. for Oesterreichische’s Exportförderunginstitut 33-38. Hobby: art.
